                        <p class="Para">Reputation systems play an important role in many Internet communities. They allow individuals to estimate other individualâ€™s behavior during interactions. However, a more privacy-friendly reputation system is desirable while maintaining its trustworthiness.</p>
                        <p class="Para">This paper presents a fair anonymous submission and review system. The review process is reputation-based and provides better anonymity properties than existing reputation systems. Moreover, the system allows for accountability measures. Anonymous credentials are used as basic blocks.</p>
